.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, comedy, crime, fantasy
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, folk, reggae, soul
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, lacrosse, tennis
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, boat, quad-bike, snowmobile
 1. the person watching crime movies is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 3. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 4. the person watching documentary movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
 6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
 7. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
 8. the person driving the boat is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 9. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
10. the person watching comedy movies is not to the right of the fan of folk##8
11. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
12. the person driving the snowmobile is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cycling##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre      | documentary   | fantasy     | crime    | comedy |
| Music-Genre   | ambient  | soul      | reggae     | folk     |
| Sport         | climbing | lacrosse  | tennis     | cycling  |
| Transport     | bike     | quad-bike | snowmobile | boat     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, juice, soy-milk, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, chess, magic-tricks, skydiving
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, house, indie, trance
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, animation, mystery, superhero
 1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 2. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
 3. the person drinking sprite is the fan of house##1
 4. the fan of house is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
 5. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the fan of trance##5
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the left of the fan of dubstep##8
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
 8. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
 9. the person watching animation movies is not to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
10. the fan of indie is not the person watching horror movies##6
11. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
12. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
13. the fan of trance is not to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
14. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | cola      | sprite  | soy-milk | juice        |
| Hobby         | skydiving | chess   | baking   | magic-tricks |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | house   | indie    | dubstep      |
| Movie-Genre   | animation   | superhero | mystery   | horror    |

