.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, milk, sprite
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, electrician, musician, police-officer
4 different pets are kept: goat, hedgehog, pony, snake
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, cain, bongani, siglo
 1. the bongani-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 2. the owner of the snake is not to the right of the electrician##8
 3. the owner of the goat is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 4. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the owner of the pony##5
 6. the siglo-smoker is the person drinking juice##1
 7. the police-officer is not to the right of the siglo-smoker##8
 8. the musician is on the far right##1
 9. the electrician is not to the right of the person drinking milk##8
10. the bolivar-smoker is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the snake##5
12. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5
13. the bongani-smoker is not to the left of the police-officer##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1        |    2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | juice          | iced-tea | milk        | sprite    |
| Job         | police-officer | doctor   | electrician | musician  |
| Pet         | pony           | goat     | snake       | hedgehog  |
| Cigar   | siglo            | bongani   | cain     | bolivar |

